          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High purity titanium sponge (99.999% pure), weighing",
                " 25-50 mg, was filled in a quartz ampoule, sealed and",
                " then placed in an NRX type aluminum irradiation",
                " capsule.",
                "Two of each of the three neutron flux monitor foils",
                " (Au, Fe and Ni) were placed in a cylindrical",
                " arrangement around the ampoule in such a way that the",
                " same neutron flux monitor material was on opposite",
                " sides of the ampoule, allowing thereby a",
                " determination of the effective flux density within",
                " the ampoule.",
                "The foils were washed with acetone; dried and weighed",
                " before attaching to the ampoules."
              ]
            }
          ],
